{"tid":1649981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"識玩既一定用電話, 你今日call 佐未?","createTime":"2019-10-12T19:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T02:39:17.000Z","uid":319687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a616c652a2c39336e58fe2a92bda5e9cdbdcc72","tid":1649981,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:19:31.000Z","msg":"而家POPO接一個投訢電話<br />\n就借機會派幾十個防暴衝去一個屋苑捉人<br />\n我地何不借呢個機會去效法呢D<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以其人之道還自其人之身?</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>玩法1: 提供線索比呀蛇</strong></ins><br />\n每人每日直接打電話比POPO, 比D線索佢地捉呢D黑衣暴徒<br />\n記住要開張新既電話卡<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>玩法2: 幫呀蛇叫外賣</strong></ins><br />\n每人每日直接打電話幫呀蛇叫外賣, 慰勞下咁鮮苦既呀蛇<br />\n可以直接落去狗屋, 或者幫呀蛇屋企人叫<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>玩法3: 振興藍絲外賣生意</strong></ins><br />\n每人每日直接打電話叫外賣, 促進香港經濟, 共享中共帶黎既和平<br />\n可以幫Popo 民建聯, 中聯辦落外賣, 共建<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲經濟圈</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實除佐外賣之外, 仲有好多唔同既上門服務, 送貨服務<br />\n大家不坊可以每日試足咁多個選擇<br />\n促進香港經濟, 呀蛇又有好既服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a234dc0e7343e32300259cbd475e9c7b0874fb","tid":1649981,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:31:24.000Z","msg":"不篤灰 不割蓆唔係口號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMrUgfE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMrUgfE.jpg&h=7e0b4b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8OfK8Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8OfK8Z.jpg&h=8241555a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Gc0WfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Gc0WfF.png&h=b642bb0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XmEywO1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXmEywO1.png&h=04d87e0f&s